(## 9. What to do when something fails) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `validate-stack` says API key missing:) Tj
T*
(  - set `OPENAI_API_KEY` in the same shell session) Tj
T*
(- `validate-stack` says pgvector DSN missing:) Tj
T*
(  - set `SEAM_PGVECTOR_DSN`) Tj
T*
(- `validate-stack` reports `HTTP 429`:) Tj
T*
(  - provider wiring is working, but quota/rate/billing needs attention) Tj
T*
(- `stats` regresses:) Tj
T*
(  - inspect the fixture-level `expected_ids`, `rejected_ids`, and `rejection_rate`) Tj
T*
(- search finds the right thing but also stale junk:) Tj
T*
(  - add or strengthen a benchmark fixture instead of relying on memory) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
